org.wallerlab.yoink.regionizer.partitioner

Class CubePartitioner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wallerlab.yoink.regionizer.partitioner.CubePartitioner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Partitioner<java.util.List<GridPoint>,DensityPoint.DensityType>

    @Service
public class CubePartitioner
extends java.lang.Object
implements Partitioner<java.util.List<GridPoint>,DensityPoint.DensityType>
    This class is to get those grid points that belong to the intersection region of QM core region and non-QM core region. Then further calculation(dori and sedd) will just be carried out on those grid points.
